    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【大纲】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>这是什麽鬼学校啊？！</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/e3c7e7affbee9a1bb9523966f90b4832.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夏海在转学的第一天就遇到各种奇怪的事情：突然就找碴的辅导老师，信仰狂热的校长，超脱常理观念的同学们…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一开学就面对这些过度有个性的同学与老师，她有办法适应接下来的学校生活吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游玩方式】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/bdd67ffb76f3c890754c321ca31f341b.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=439 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲游戏目标：玩家需要在20日以内将学力与体力提升到20以上！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.poster.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.webm?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/12ee925355d8b0aebc24cddece4c0105.mp4?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲用上下左右操控夏海移动，并且使用Z键跟各种同学与老师互动吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.poster.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.webm?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b083b97e684d422a0fde841e2f89a0f2.mp4?t=1762827506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲认真上课，增加自己的学力吧！虽然有时候可能会遇到意外而得自习...？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲因为这是个奇怪的学校，所以你还得跟同学切磋武艺喔！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/b6ad5f1a445b607cc7b5f1f62ad4c753.avif?t=1762827506\" width=600 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲努力活用学校的各项机能提升自己的能力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【主角介绍】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/6d0d79ef46176f25cd6085d2f16c5b90.avif?t=1762827506\" width=254 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲夏海</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平凡的女孩子，由于爸爸出国工作所以暂住在奶奶家中。<br>刚转学到新学校，心中有些紧张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【配角介绍】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/f4aa5b36f215c407eafb5df604b1787e.avif?t=1762827506\" width=616 height=450 /></span></p>",
